Database Project
Overview

This project demonstrates how to execute SQL scripts automatically using Jenkins pipeline.

The Jenkins pipeline clones the repository from GitHub and runs the SQL script on a database.

Technologies Used

Git

Jenkins

MySQL

Project Structure

database_project
├── Jenkinsfile
├── script.sql
└── README.md

How It Works

Developer pushes code to GitHub.

Jenkins pipeline is triggered.

Jenkins clones the repository.

Jenkins executes the SQL script.

The database is updated automatically.
